"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Culiac\u00e1n in northern Mexico has seen a surge in violence as rival factions of the Sinaloa cartel battle for control. BBC international correspondent Quentin Sommerville travelled to Culiac\u00e1n in northern Sinaloa state following an explosion in violence.\",            \"english_title\": \"Violence in Culiac\u00e1n\",            \"translated_version\": \"Culiac\u00e1n en el norte de M\u00e9xico ha visto m\u00e1s violencia porque grupos rivales del cartel de Sinaloa pelean por el control. El corresponsal internacional de la BBC, Quentin Sommerville, viaj\u00f3 a Culiac\u00e1n en el estado de Sinaloa despu\u00e9s de una explosi\u00f3n de violencia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Violencia en Culiac\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The next round of talks between the US and Iran in Geneva on Thursday could be decisive in the president's decision-making.\",            \"english_title\": \"US-Iran Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"La pr\u00f3xima ronda de conversaciones entre Estados Unidos e Ir\u00e1n en Ginebra el jueves podr\u00eda ser decisiva en las decisiones del presidente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones EEUU-Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A newspaper reports Gates apologised to staff over his links to Epstein and said: 'I did nothing illicit. I saw nothing illicit.'\",            \"english_title\": \"Gates Apologises\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un peri\u00f3dico informa que Gates se disculp\u00f3 con el personal por sus v\u00ednculos con Epstein y dijo: `No hice nada ilegal. No vi nada ilegal.`\",            \"translated_title\": \"Gates se Disculpa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Marielle Franco's murder at the age of 38 in Rio de Janeiro sparked protests across Brazil.\",            \"english_title\": \"Marielle Franco's Murder\",            \"translated_version\": \"El asesinato de Marielle Franco a los 38 a\u00f1os en R\u00edo de Janeiro provoc\u00f3 protestas en todo Brasil.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Asesinato de Marielle Franco\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The remote Yonaguni island lies on the frontlines of self-governing Taiwan's growing tensions with China.\",            \"english_title\": \"Yonaguni Island Tensions\",            \"translated_version\": \"La isla remota de Yonaguni est\u00e1 en la primera l\u00ednea de las crecientes tensiones de Taiw\u00e1n con China.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tensiones en Isla Yonaguni\"        }    ]}"